NOTICE OF ASSESSMENT LIEN
SCANNED
Christina Munoz
Great Northwest Community Improvement Association, Inc.
$1,743.59 ($1,178.59* homeowner assessments and late fees;
$565.00 attorney's fees and expenses)
*Does not include an annual assessment of $293.00 levied January
1, 2022
8374 Timber Cabin, San Antonio, Texas 78250
Lot 71, Block 37, New City Block 18737, Great Northwest
Subdivision, Unit 26, Bexar County, Texas
Notice is hereby given that the above-described Property is encumbered and subject to indebtedness owed to the
lien holder by the Owner in the amount set forth above for due but unpaid assessments, late fees, legal expenses, and filing
fees, and that pursuant to the Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Great Northwest Subdivision,
executed on March 24, 1976, recorded in Volume 7783, Page 598, Official Public Records of Real Property of Bexar
County, Texas, as amended by the Amendment to Declaration of Covenants, Conditions and Restrictions for Great
Northwest Subdivision, executed on March 23, 1977, recorded in Volume 8171, Page 357, Official Public Records of Real
Property of Bexar County, Texas, as further amended by Certificate of Annexation to Declaration of Covenants,
Conditions and Restrictions for Great Northwest Subdivision, (Unit 26), executed on July 6, 1983, recorded in Volume
2883, Page 350, Official Public Records of Real Property of Bexar County, Texas as amended, the lien holder has a Lien
on the Property described above for said sums.
Notice is further given that the amount of the Lien continues to increase pursuant to the terms of the
referenced Declaration.
Executed this
13 thday of Fantasy
, 2022.
GREAT NORTHWEST COMMUNITY
IMPROVEMENT ASSOCIATION, INC .,
a Texas non-profit corporation
STATE OF TEXAS
COUNTY OF BEXAR $
Lexi Bachran, Manager
Great Northwest Community Improvement Association, Inc.
8809 Timberwilde Drive
San Antonio, TX 78250
Before me, the undersigned notary public, on this day personally appeared Lexi Bachran acting on
behalf of GREAT NORTHWEST COMMUNITY IMPROVEMENT ASSOCIATION, INC ., known to me or
proved to me by presentation to me of a governmentally-issued identification card to be the person whose name
is subscribed to the foregoing instrument, and acknowledged to me that they executed it for the purposes and
consideration expressed in it.
Given under my hand and seal of office the 1 3
yor Jamany 2022
